The StatsMgr is used to control the gathering of device usage statistics, set the name and location of the statistics file and its reporting interval, and clear saved data. 

### Main Functionality

* Enable/Disable usage statistics
* Set the Reporting Interval
* Set the name and location of the statistics file 
* Clear data saved in the statistics file

